Subject: [PATCH 2/2] as3645a: Add driver for LED flash controller
Date: Fri,  9 Sep 2011 17:52:49 +0200
Message-Id: <1315583569-22727-3-git-send-email-laurent.pinchart@ideasonboard.com>
In-Reply-To: <1315583569-22727-1-git-send-email-laurent.pinchart@ideasonboard.com>
